Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Radio] Manta 5-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue your approach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to Atlas docking bay, Omega-12.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A security team will meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- But we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the lamp to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess we land and get some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen our forces\Ndeployed so aggressively before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we land in a stolen ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way the security team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,will let us anywhere near Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They might even take me back to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Put some distance\Nbetween us and the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't have to tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Braodcast] ...cannot express\Nour appreciation enough....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Many describe these as uncertain times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and while that may be the case\Nfor the rest of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you what is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kingdom of Atlas will remain strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will remain safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- General Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- James, what have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian 1] Ugh, not these again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Civilian 2] Why can't\Nthey just leave us be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Radio] Manta 5-1, we've\Nnoticed a detour in your route.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to make your way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to docking bay Omega-12\Nimmediately, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're kind of running\Nout of time here, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- We need to ditch the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost in Mantle and\Nbuy ourselves some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm telling you, my sister\Ncan take us to Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh, Weiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Broadcast] A reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Failure to cooperate with\NAtlas military personnel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is a punishable offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If your sector
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is under lockdown...\N- Winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- No offense, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure that's a good idea anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's obviously something very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can just talk to her, then we--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look, I'm not even sure we\Nshould be talking to Ironwood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,until we know exactly\Nwhat's going on with Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- But--\N- Everyone, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,(sighs) I know someone\Nwho can help with both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Radio] Manta 5-1, you are to make your-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jeez, lady, take a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Soldier] It landed\Nover there, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be much of a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this many soldiers normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should pick up the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have to remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the kingdom had just lost the Great War.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Mantle needed\Na sign of a brighter future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and that sign was Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, a home in the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is about as bright as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Unless you're the one\Nhaving to look up at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- This whole city, it just seems awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of space out in the tundra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry, I didn't mean to-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Atlas is the greatest kingdom\Nin the world, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- We can't cause a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- The embargo-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the embargo's got us in a rough patch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but it'll blow over, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- We try and help the other kingdoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I say let 'em rot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to insult you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stupid Faunus like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't under-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that was-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- We are here for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Man] And no more heavy lifting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, it's good to see you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, this is off to a fantastic start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cybernetic optical implants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You adjust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Every 10 years or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with the cybernetic optical implants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I adjust them every 10 years or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(laughing) Oh wow, has it\Nbeen that long already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I age like a fine wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would've been here sooner if I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,run into these jokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they might need my guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,while fighting a little old sphinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They had much more complicated issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- (clearing throat) And this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- So impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd need\Nto introduce one of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas' finest minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Working in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- He likes to keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I've come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,none of you know anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can call me Pietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Finest heart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This pharmacy is just where he volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when he's not building the future of Atlas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,alongside Ironwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,up in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, it's stuffy up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here I get to help the locals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a little fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently working on shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that make you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna try 'em on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Before we get to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we were wondering if you could help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to Atlas hoping to\Ntalk with General Ironwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- What exactly has been happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- (coughing) Well, the\Nfall of Beacon took a toll
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,James was no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you exactly what it was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but it changed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Paranoid would be the\Nmore appropriate term.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't just the Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone completely dismantled\NAtlas security code.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it their play-thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And made us look like traitors to some and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,buffoons to everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever managed to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is either a genius or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear the answer may be both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so does the General.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe Atlas isn't as safe as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- After we came all this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't just leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- How does the council\Nfeel about all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Winter Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, the council's so scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll agree to whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though some representatives from Mantle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're Weiss Schnee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, what was it that you were trying
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to say about Mantle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- You painted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're Team RWBY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, my girl I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I most certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like such a\Ndunce for not recognizing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter's told me so much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your... daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- I guess the city\Ndefenses aren't doing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Somehow that doesn't surprise me.
