Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you say hello to your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sal-
