Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,TATIONS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is such a pleasure\Nto see you all again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny, I-
